{"tid":1771423,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"曾支持反送中運動台灣歌手謝和弦 遭妻子檢舉吸毒被捕","createTime":"2019-12-06T00:50:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-24T18:31:55.000Z","uid":242050,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"5d3fd5ba5d42ccf88254906702c8f2c5329f59b0","tid":1771423,"uid":242050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:50:54.000Z","msg":"台灣歌手「搖滾壞小子」謝和弦昨晚涉吸食大麻被捕，警方接舉報到達其住所，並搜獲約18克疑似大麻物品，謝和弦承認疑似大麻物品是他管有，隨即被帶返警署調查。而當中舉報人竟然是其妻子戴怡軒（Keanna）！<br />\n2012年謝和弦曾於Facebook自爆吸食大麻，更留言：「等你們來抓我，我在埔里的老家，我去打電動了，掰。」其後他到警局自首，事後遭唱片公司解約，更被謝父爆料有躁鬱症病史，謝和弦演藝事業因而一度暫停。<br />\n謝和弦2017年與台荷混血女友Keanna結婚，婚後Keanna曾在臉書上坦承老公「不對勁」，有指Keanna一直協助謝和弦重新做人，不忍老公再次沉淪毒海，故報警大義滅親。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jgybSjT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjgybSjT.png&h=fe106aa3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9efd2cb13ede5a9f1136f4abb5232fcaaa53ae8","tid":1771423,"uid":321674,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:52:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e770163554aaef4e2b3780d8e0d3b22e5a8b69d9","tid":1771423,"uid":13375,"like":30,"dislike":8,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:53:41.000Z","msg":"打band 隊草都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be9568b531d874fce18d5f419b248ac9bdd6eec9","tid":1771423,"uid":225130,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:54:57.000Z","msg":"呢條友都癲癲地架啦"},{"pid":"cada92f471640d605fc7a8dca6e02c8f7052f614","tid":1771423,"uid":321674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T00:57:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c60a14e3e47540a4b7b095bbb2b696e4cd510ed3","tid":1771423,"uid":133033,"like":39,"dislike":1,"score":38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-06T01:07:01.000Z","msg":"屌⋯ 佢日日都表態支持架 連登仔"},{"pid":"2f0c7029281f3595315e379be38411a535672640","t